Subject: Re: [VB] No idle, delayed motor racing after throttle

Try using carb cleaner to check for leaks instead of WD40. Make sure it 
has a nice big Flammable warning label. It sounds like a huge vacuum 
leak, probably between the manifold and head. Check the boot on the 
manifold too.

John Yust
'65 Deluxe
'65 Crewcab

